{"tid":1660682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好搞清真寺重慶大廈","createTime":"2019-10-17T15:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:14:28.000Z","uid":316813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98239447900aa43fbb26e13550e2d7da7cee695f","tid":1660682,"uid":316813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"今個星期日大家出來 出埋岑子杰果份 <br />\n和理非懇請唔好裝修充慶大廈，清真寺<br />\n<br />\n1) 南亞都好多唔同種族，襲擊都明顯唔關宗教事而係買兇，唔好禍及無辜<br />\n2) 美國法案未正式過，如果搞著宗教場所，穆斯林信徒嘅話驚炒車❗❗<br />\n3) 仆街無分國籍<br />\n何妖777㩒制派係(奶共)香港人 <br />\n反而女神利君雅都係少數族裔架<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都知道唔好搞佢地架啦，如果見到手足衝動幫手叫停好無?<br />\n<br />\n幫手推文可以嗎 謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0gRcSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0gRcSq.jpg&h=e39cfddc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b917f391822b72fc35f71562c0c3ca2bf80d308d","tid":1660682,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5e26ca43c119c0f695a09a30c24f984c60bce6be","tid":1660682,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"「連登淪陷4.0 」中共利用香港人唯一嘅弱點主慢慢開始局部瓦解！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660643</a>"},{"pid":"3ea0bc708a877f4718300b7753918cbe718ea649","tid":1660682,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"邊個搞重慶/清真寺嘅話大家可以立即召喚神獸鶳了"}]}